  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EEFGroupDescription, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EStructuralFeature.Internal.DynamicValueHolder, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.InternalEObject

    public class EEFGroupDescriptionImpl
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.impl.MinimalEObjectImpl.Container
implements EEFGroupDescription
    An implementation of the model object 'EEF Group Description'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Identifier
    • Label Expression
    • Domain Class
    • Semantic Candidate Expression
    • Precondition Expression
    • Controls
    • Semantic Validation Rules
    • Property Validation Rules
    • Style
    • Conditional Styles
    • Actions
